snippet.title: Radio Viscera - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Travel back to 1999 and topple a doomsday cult in a chaotic, blood-soaked arcade adventure game where the walls are only a temporary obstacle...
Coming soon - Wishlist now at http://RadioViscera.com

Follow https://twitter.com/owendeery for more behind-the-scenes content and developer updates
